bt_graticule.Rd

Graticules

Usage

bt_graticule(bertin, strokeWidth, strokeDasharray, stroke, step, ...)

Arguments

bertin

map object

strokeWidth

str wid

strokeDasharray

str dash arr

stroke

str

step

step

...

other param

Value

map object

Examples

library(sf)
world <- st_read(system.file("gpkg/world.gpkg", package = "bertin"),
                 layer = "world", quiet = TRUE)
bt_param(margin = 10, width = 500, projection = "Winkel3") |>
  bt_layer(data = world, fill = "red") |>
  bt_graticule(strokeWidth = 1.5, stroke  = "green", step  = 15)|>
  bt_draw()
